flowchart LR
    has_custom{customSystemPrompt\n已设置?}
    
    has_custom -->|否| normal_path[正常路径]
    normal_path --> dp[defaultSystemPrompt\n工具声明+核心指令]
    normal_path --> uc[userContext\nCLAUDE.md内容]
    normal_path --> sc[systemContext\n环境上下文]
    
    has_custom -->|是| custom_path[覆盖路径]
    custom_path --> empty_dp["defaultSystemPrompt = []"]
    custom_path --> uc2["userContext = CLAUDE.md\n（仍然生效）"]
    custom_path --> empty_sc["systemContext = {}"]
